### All requests go through the API Gateway (port 5000)
@gateway = http://localhost:5000

### Login as admin first (write operations require the Admin role)
# @name adminLogin
POST {{gateway}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ecommerce.dev",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### List categories (public)
# @name categories
GET {{gateway}}/api/categories

### Create a product (Admin) — publishes ProductCreated via the transactional outbox
POST {{gateway}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",
  "description": "Apple flagship smartphone with titanium design",
  "price": 1299.99,
  "categoryId": "{{categories.response.body.$[0].id}}"
}

### List products (public, paged)
GET {{gateway}}/api/products?page=1&pageSize=20

### Product detail (served from Redis cache after first hit)
GET {{gateway}}/api/products/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Change price (Admin) — publishes ProductPriceChanged, Search index follows
PATCH {{gateway}}/api/products/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/price
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newPrice": 1199.99
}

### Full-text search (Elasticsearch, fed by Catalog events)
GET {{gateway}}/api/search?q=iphone

### Search with filters and sorting
GET {{gateway}}/api/search?q=phone&minPrice=500&maxPrice=2000&sort=price_asc&page=1&pageSize=10
